<p>Hi <%= @member.name %>,</p>

<p>
  Great news! <strong><%= @church.name %></strong> is now <strong>active</strong> on FreelyShared!
  Your church community is ready to start sharing goods and offering skills to serve one another.
</p>

<p>Sign in now to browse what's available, list items to share, or offer your skills:</p>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="<%= new_church_member_session_url %>" class="btn">Sign In to FreelyShared</a>
</p>

<p>
  Spread the word! Invite other members of <%= @church.name %> to join at:<br>
  <a href="<%= church_url(@church) %>"><%= church_url(@church) %></a>
</p>

<p style="text-align: center; margin: 24px 0; color: #6c757d;">
  <em>"All the believers were one in heart and mind. No one claimed that any of their
  possessions was their own, but they shared everything they had."</em><br>
  <strong>— Acts 4:32</strong>
</p>
